node.text:
We asked for better content creation. @offensivegroup delivered. 

In this cinematic experience, RUSH: ALPHA TEAM, a special forces team is deployed to eliminate hostile creatures beneath the Earth’s surface. We won't spoil it for you, but they are carrying HKs ;)

Enjoy...

@eotech @agmglobalvision @hecklerandkoch @silencerco @arisakadefense @_opscore @geissele @511tactical @revisionmilitary @core_survival @lag_tactical @ertactical
